2001-08-14  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* zfstream.h, zfilebuf.h, zfilebuf.cc, zfPdbstream.h, zfBinstream.h, sockbuf.h, sockbuf.cc, sBinstream.h, fPdbstream.h, fBinstream.h, ServerSocket.h, ServerSocket.cc, ResidueTypeImp.h, ResidueTypeImp.cc, ResidueType.h, Pdbstream.h, Pdbstream.cc, McCore.h, McCore.cc, Makefile.in, DirectedGraph.h, DirectedGraph.cc, CTransfo.h, CTransfo.cc, CResidue.h, CResidue.cc, CResIdSet.h, CResIdSet.cc, CResId.h, CResId.cc, CPoint3D.h, CPoint3D.cc, CModel.h, CModel.cc, CMessageQueue.h, CMessageQueue.cc, CHBond.h, CHBond.cc, CGraph.h, CException.h, CException.cc, CAtom.h, CAtom.cc, Binstream.h, Binstream.cc, AtomTypeImp.h, AtomTypeImp.cc, AtomType.h, Algo.h, Algo.cc:
	Copyright notice includes Université de Montréal.

2001-08-08  Philippe Thibault  <thibaup@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CAtom.cc: fixed a minor bug in class constructors

2001-07-25  Sebastien Lemieux  <lemieuxs@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CHBond.cc: Reactivated method 'DumpAmberRestraints'.

	* McCore.h, McCore.cc: Modified the function 'rmsd_with_align' to
	take two pairs of templated iterator.  The only constraint on the
	iterators is that they should be dereferencable to 'CAtom's.  This
	allows to compute RMSD on any type of container and both on CAtom*
	or CResidue::iterator.  The function was split between the .h and
	.cc to minimize the compilation effort...

	* CHBond.cc, Algo.h, Algo.cc: dummy

	* CResidue.h: Added data member 'mExternalIndex' with Get/Set.

	* Pdbstream.cc: Removed the possibility to write 'HETATM' in
	function 'putatom'.  Interfer with the use of rt_Misc in 'toleap'
	package.

2001-07-16  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* Algo.h: FLT_MAX replaced with HUGE.

2001-07-05  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CResidue.cc, CResidue.h, sockbuf.h:
	Corrected the AtomCopy function so that iterators stay valid

2001-06-21  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* Algo.h, CHBond.cc, CHBond.h, CModel.h, DirectedGraph.h, McCore.cc, McCore.h:
	Modified CHBond and added an inheritance from HBond, which is a symbolic description only

2001-05-29  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* CHBond.h, CModel.cc, CModel.h, CResidue.cc, CResidue.h, CTransfo.cc, CTransfo.h, DirectedGraph.cc, DirectedGraph.h, Makefile.in, McCore.cc, McCore.h, CAtom.cc, CAtom.h, CHBond.cc:
	Corrected some bugs in CResidue due to isIdentity

2001-05-28  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* McCore.h, McCore.cc, CResidue.h, CResidue.cc, CModel.h, CModel.cc:
	Modified the rmsd function for const_iterator.

2001-05-28  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/CModel.h, lib/CModel.cc: sortAtoms is no longer needed since
	the atoms in the residue are already sorted.

	* lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc: The residue is no longer lazy
	but semi lazy.  On the first request to an atom, all the atoms of
	the residue are placed in local referential.  On const_iterator,
	the atom in global reference is returned if the transfo is the
	identity.

2001-05-28  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* lib/CAtom.cc, lib/CAtom.h, lib/CHBond.cc, lib/CHBond.h, lib/CModel.h, lib/CResidue.cc, lib/CResidue.h, lib/DirectedGraph.cc, lib/DirectedGraph.h, lib/Makefile.in, lib/McCore.cc, lib/McCore.h:
	Added a directed graph class and the CHBond for LW+ pairings

	* lib/DirectedGraph.cc, lib/DirectedGraph.h: New file.

2001-05-15  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/ResidueTypeImp.cc, lib/AtomTypeImp.cc: The type are saved in
	a int form for compatibility with jmccore.

2001-05-11  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/zfstream.h, lib/zfilebuf.h, lib/zfilebuf.cc, lib/zfPdbstream.h, lib/zfBinstream.h, lib/sockbuf.h, lib/sockbuf.cc, lib/sBinstream.h, lib/fPdbstream.h, lib/fBinstream.h, lib/ServerSocket.h, lib/ServerSocket.cc, lib/ResidueTypeImp.h, lib/ResidueTypeImp.cc, lib/ResidueType.h, lib/Pdbstream.h, lib/Pdbstream.cc, lib/McCore.h, lib/McCore.cc, lib/Makefile.in, lib/CTransfo.h, lib/CTransfo.cc, lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc, lib/CResIdSet.h, lib/CResIdSet.cc, lib/CResId.h, lib/CResId.cc, lib/CPoint3D.h, lib/CPoint3D.cc, lib/CModel.h, lib/CModel.cc, lib/CMessageQueue.h, lib/CMessageQueue.cc, lib/CHBond.h, lib/CHBond.cc, lib/CGraph.h, lib/CException.h, lib/CException.cc, lib/CAtom.h, lib/CAtom.cc, lib/Binstream.h, lib/Binstream.cc, lib/AtomTypeImp.h, lib/AtomTypeImp.cc, lib/AtomType.h, lib/Algo.h, lib/Algo.cc, configure.in, COPYING:
