	* lib/ResidueTypeImp.h, lib/ResidueTypeImp.cc, lib/ResidueType.h, lib/Pdbstream.cc, lib/McCore.cc, lib/Makefile.in, lib/CResidue.cc, lib/AtomTypeImp.h, lib/AtomTypeImp.cc, lib/AtomType.h:
	AtomType and ResidueType implementation separated from the interface.

2001-02-28  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/Pdbstream.h, lib/Pdbstream.cc: atomsetopt removed.

2001-02-21  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* lib/CResidue.cc, lib/CResidue.h: The residue reserves space for
	mAtomRes

	* lib/Algo.h: Corrected a bug when the model contains no contact

2001-02-21  Sebastien Lemieux  <lemieuxs@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* lib/CResidue.cc, lib/CResidue.h: CResidue::Align now correctly
	resets the transformed atoms positions.

2001-02-14  Sebastien Lemieux  <lemieuxs@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* lib/Makefile.in: dummy

	* lib/Algo.cc: See comment on Algo.h

	* lib/Algo.h: Algo class is used to encapsulate algorithms on
	McCore data structure.  This initial version contain
	'ExtractContact_AABB' allowing to extract contacts on a structure
	using axis aligned bounding boxes.

	* lib/CPoint3D.h: Added method 'Get(int)' allowing to deal with a
	point as a vector.

2001-02-09  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/CResIdSet.cc, lib/CResId.cc: Nouveau lexique pour les
	residue id: '<char>'<no> | <char><no> | <no>.

	* lib/CAtom.h: Operator != added for atom and type comparison.

	* docs/McCoreManual.tex, docs/Makefile.in: Manual added.

	* lib/Makefile.in: headers installed in include/mcccore-$(VERSION)
	directory.  Version number added in the libraries.

	* lib/Pdbstream.h: Comments removed.

	* lib/CMessageQueue.h: Output operator added for ostream and ios
	functions.

2001-02-05  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/CModel.cc: Iteration bug in operator[] corrected.

2001-02-02  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/McCore.cc, lib/Pdbstream.cc, lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc, lib/CModel.cc, lib/CAtom.h, configure.in, configure:
	Temporary update.

2001-01-24  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/CResidue.cc: Validate removes the second residue of a duplicate.

2001-01-23  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/Pdbstream.h, lib/Pdbstream.cc, lib/McCore.h, lib/McCore.cc, lib/Makefile.in, lib/CTransfo.h, lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc, lib/CResIdSet.h, lib/CResId.h, lib/CResId.cc, lib/CPoint3D.h, lib/CPoint3D.cc, lib/CModel.h, lib/CModel.cc, lib/CMessageQueue.h, lib/CMessageQueue.cc, lib/CException.h, lib/CAtom.h, lib/CAtom.cc, lib/Binstream.h, lib/Binstream.cc, lib/AtomType.h, lib/AtomType.cc:
	Documentation enhancement.

2001-01-22  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/Binstream.h, lib/Binstream.cc: The binstream are back with
	swap_endian.  ntohl and htonl are incompatible with older versions
	of the database.

	* lib/zfBinstream.h: Cyclic call to izfBinstream close call corrected.

	* lib/Pdbstream.h, lib/Pdbstream.cc, lib/McCore.h, lib/McCore.cc:
	Amino acid names modified.

	* lib/CTransfo.h: *** empty log message ***

	* lib/CResidue.cc: Output added in Validate method.

	* lib/CResidue.h: *** empty log message ***

	* lib/CResId.h, lib/CResId.cc: operator const char* added.

	* lib/CPoint3D.h, lib/CPoint3D.cc: *** empty log message ***

	* lib/CModel.h, lib/CModel.cc: A model is now a list of residues.

	* lib/CAtom.h, lib/CAtom.cc: AtomSet binary saving added.

	* lib/Binstream.h: operator<< and operator>> defined over booleans.

	* lib/AtomType.h: Naming corrections over some amino acids.
	AmberRep method is added.

	* lib/AtomType.cc: Naming corrections over some amino acids.

2000-12-04  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/Pdbstream.h: GetAtomType is now public.

	* lib/Pdbstream.cc: Bug correction: PSY and PSZ were considered as
	Misc atoms.

	* lib/CResidue.cc: Explicit call to AtomSet operator().

	* lib/CResIdSet.cc: Code transfered to CResId constructor.

	* lib/CResId.h, lib/CResId.cc: Constructor over string
	representation added.

	* lib/CPoint3D.cc: Test over 0 divisor to prevent crash.

	* lib/CModel.h, lib/CModel.cc: find methods added.

	* lib/CAtom.h: AtomSet clone and evaluation functions corrected.

2000-12-01  Patrick Gendron  <gendrop@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* lib/CResIdSet.cc: Corrrected a bug in CResIdSet output

2000-11-22  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc: The second AtomSet function is
	removed from the iterators.  It can be replaced by the conjunction
	atomset_and.

	* lib/CTransfo.h: RMS_align method removed.

	* lib/McCore.h, lib/McCore.cc: Magnesium, MG, 1H, 2H and 3H atom
	types and objects added.  gMcLicenseDir variable pointing to the
	license directory added.

	* lib/CResidue.cc: Partial corrections over iterator increments
	made.  More to come.

	* lib/Pdbstream.cc, lib/AtomType.h, lib/AtomType.cc: Magnesium,
	MG, 1H, 2H and 3H atom added.  Corrections over is_connected and
	GetAtomType made for amino acids.

2000-11-14  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/McCore.h, lib/McCore.cc, lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc:
	iterator inlining done.

	* lib/CResidue.cc: Iterator bug corrected.  The mPos might be
	higher than the size of the atom vector.

2000-11-10  Labo Lbit  <adbit@mansarde.IRO.UMontreal.CA>

	* lib/CResIdSet.cc: McCore header needed.

	* lib/CResidue.h: typedef made public for irix compilation.

2000-11-09  Martin Larose  <larosem@iro.umontreal.ca>

	* lib/McCore.h, lib/McCore.cc, lib/CResidue.h, lib/CResidue.cc:
	Correction on CResidue iterators to facilitate sgi compilation.

